metadata.name: Shaya the Martian Warrior
metadata.description:
Shaya, a timid young girl, has had to face a hostile environment and learn to survive where others have perished. 
Shaya must go beyond human endurance, uncover the dark secrets of the forgotten planet of Mars to which fate has cast her, and fight for her right to escape the place's deadly grip.

JPG, 4000x5000 px
